        "headline": "Columbia’s operating surplus drops to $112.6 million as expenses outpace revenue growth",
        "dek": "Revenue grew 2.1 percent while expenses climbed 5.3 percent, driving a $192 million drop in the University’s operating surplus, according to its recent financial report.",
